---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Global Markets | Victoria Herbs & Spices – Exporting Kenyan Herbs Worldwide"
  description="Victoria Herbs & Spices exports premium Kenyan herbs and spices to Europe, North America, and Asia. FDA compliant, EU certified, and CFIA approved. Trusted by importers across three continents."
>
  <!-- Hero Section - Global Reach -->
  <section
    class="relative h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
  >
    <!-- Background with world map impression -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589519160732-57fc6ea83bc8?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80"
        alt="World map with spices"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-stone-900/90 via-stone-900/70 to-stone-900/90"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <!-- Global Badge -->
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-amber-500/20 backdrop-blur-lg px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-amber-300 text-sm mb-8 border border-amber-500/30"
      >
        <span class="relative flex h-3 w-3">
          <span
            class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-amber-400 opacity-75"
          ></span>
          <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-amber-500"
          ></span>
        </span>
        <span>🌍 Exporting to 15+ Countries</span>
        <span class="text-white/50 mx-2">•</span>
        <span>🇰🇪 Proudly Kenyan</span>
      </div>

      <h1
        class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold text-white leading-tight"
      >
        From Kenya,<br />
        <span
          class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-orange-400"
        >
          To the World
        </span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-white/90 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Our herbs and spices have found their way to discerning importers across
        three continents — meeting and exceeding local regulations, cultural
        expectations, and quality standards.
      </p>

      <!-- Global Stats -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-10 mt-12">
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">15+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-white/70">Countries</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">3</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-white/70">Continents</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">98%</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-white/70">On-Time Delivery</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">24/7</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-white/70">Logistics Support</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center text-white/40 text-xs tracking-widest"
    >
      <span>EXPLORE MARKETS</span>
      <div
        class="w-px h-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-white/30 to-transparent mt-2"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Market Navigation -->
  <div class="bg-white border-b border-stone-200 sticky top-20 z-40">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div
        class="flex overflow-x-auto hide-scrollbar gap-8 py-4 text-sm font-medium"
      >
        <a
          href="#europe"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >🇪🇺 Europe</a
        >
        <a
          href="#north-america"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >🇺🇸 North America</a
        >
        <a
          href="#asia"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >🌏 Asia</a
        >
        <a
          href="#africa"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >🇿🇦 Africa</a
        >
        <a
          href="#middle-east"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >🕌 Middle East</a
        >
        <a
          href="#logistics"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >📦 Logistics</a
        >
        <a
          href="#certifications"
          class="text-stone-600 hover:text-amber-600 transition whitespace-nowrap"
          >✅ Certifications</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Europe Section -->
  <section id="europe" class="py-24 bg-white scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <span class="text-7xl">🇪🇺</span>
            <div>
              <span
                class="text-amber-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase"
                >Market</span
              >
              <h2
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-stone-900"
              >
                Europe
              </h2>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed">
            Europe represents our largest and most established market. From the
            spice houses of Germany to the tea blenders of the UK, European
            importers trust Victoria for consistent quality, organic
            certification, and reliable delivery.
          </p>

          <!-- Key Countries -->
          <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🇩🇪</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Germany</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Hamburg • Berlin • Munich</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🇳🇱</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Netherlands</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Rotterdam • Amsterdam</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🇬🇧</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">United Kingdom</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">London • Liverpool</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🇫🇷</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">France</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Paris • Marseille</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Compliance Badges -->
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span
              class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span>✅</span> EU Organic Certified
            </span>
            <span
              class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span>✅</span> REACH Compliant
            </span>
            <span
              class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span>✅</span> Novel Food Approved
            </span>
          </div>

          <!-- Market Stats -->
          <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">40%</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-stone-500">of total exports</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">8</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-stone-500">countries served</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">5+</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-stone-500">years partnership</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Market Card -->
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-stone-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-amber-200"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-6">
            Serving European Importers
          </h3>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-600 text-xl">✓</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Fast Transit:</span>
                <p class="text-stone-600">22-28 days Mombasa to Rotterdam</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-600 text-xl">✓</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Documentation:</span>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  EUR.1 certificates for preferential duties
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-600 text-xl">✓</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Language Support:</span>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  English, German, French documentation available
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-600 text-xl">✓</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Warehousing:</span>
                <p class="text-stone-600">Consolidation hub in Rotterdam</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a
            href="/markets/europe"
            class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700 font-semibold group"
          >
            Detailed Europe Market Guide
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- North America Section -->
  <section id="north-america" class="py-24 bg-stone-50 scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-stone-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-amber-200"
          >
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-6">
              North American Partnerships
            </h3>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-emerald-600 text-xl">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">FDA Compliance:</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-600">
                    All shipments meet FDA food safety requirements
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-emerald-600 text-xl">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">FSMA Ready:</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-600">
                    FSVP compliance and foreign supplier verification
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-emerald-600 text-xl">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Ports:</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-600">
                    NY/NJ, Los Angeles, Savannah, Vancouver, Montreal
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-emerald-600 text-xl">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Customs Broker:</span>
                  <p class="text-stone-600">
                    Pre-cleared documentation for smooth entry
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <a
              href="/markets/north-america"
              class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700 font-semibold group"
            >
              Detailed North America Market Guide
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="flex -space-x-4">
              <span class="text-7xl">🇺🇸</span>
              <span class="text-7xl">🇨🇦</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span
                class="text-amber-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase"
                >Market</span
              >
              <h2
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-stone-900"
              >
                North America
              </h2>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed">
            The United States and Canada represent our fastest-growing markets.
            With increasing demand for African superfoods and ethnic
            ingredients, North American importers value our FDA/CFIA compliance,
            organic options, and reliable supply chains.
          </p>

          <!-- Key Countries -->
          <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl">
              <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🇺🇸</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">United States</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">
                FDA compliant • 5 major ports
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl">
              <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🇨🇦</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Canada</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">CFIA approved • SFCR ready</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Compliance Badges -->
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span
              class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span>✅</span> FDA Compliant
            </span>
            <span
              class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span>✅</span> FSMA Ready
            </span>
            <span
              class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span>✅</span> CFIA Approved
            </span>
          </div>

          <!-- Market Stats -->
          <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">35%</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-stone-500">of total exports</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">2</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-stone-500">countries</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">+45%</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-stone-500">YoY growth</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Asia Section -->
  <section id="asia" class="py-24 bg-white scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <span class="text-7xl">🌏</span>
            <div>
              <span
                class="text-amber-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase"
                >Market</span
              >
              <h2
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-stone-900"
              >
                Asia
              </h2>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed">
            Asian markets have a deep appreciation for spices — and they
            recognize the unique quality of Kenyan produce. From Japan's
            exacting standards to Singapore's role as a regional hub, we're
            building lasting partnerships across the continent.
          </p>

          <!-- Key Countries -->
          <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🇯🇵</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Japan</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Tokyo • Osaka • Yokohama</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🇰🇷</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">South Korea</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Seoul • Busan</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🇸🇬</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Singapore</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Regional distribution hub</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🇲🇾</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Malaysia</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Kuala Lumpur • Penang</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Compliance Badges -->
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span
              class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span>✅</span> Japanese Import Standards
            </span>
            <span
              class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span>✅</span> Halal Certified
            </span>
            <span
              class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span>✅</span> JAS Organic
            </span>
          </div>

          <!-- Market Stats -->
          <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">15%</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-stone-500">of total exports</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">5</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-stone-500">countries</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">+60%</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-stone-500">growth (2024)</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Market Card -->
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-stone-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-amber-200"
        >
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-6">
            Asian Market Requirements
          </h3>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-600 text-xl">✓</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Documentation:</span>
                <p class="text-stone-600">
                  Phytosanitary certificates, origin certificates
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-600 text-xl">✓</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Packaging:</span>
                <p class="text-stone-600">Custom labeling for each market</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-600 text-xl">✓</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Quality Standards:</span>
                <p class="text-stone-600">Japanese Grade A inspection ready</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-600 text-xl">✓</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">Transit Time:</span>
                <p class="text-stone-600">25-35 days to major Asian ports</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a
            href="/markets/asia"
            class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700 font-semibold group"
          >
            Detailed Asia Market Guide
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Africa & Middle East Overview -->
  <section id="africa" class="py-24 bg-stone-50 scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Africa -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <span class="text-7xl">🇿🇦</span>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-stone-900">
              Africa
            </h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-stone-700 mb-6">
            Growing regional demand for Kenyan herbs and spices, particularly in
            South Africa, Nigeria, and neighboring East African countries.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-3 rounded-lg">
              <span class="font-bold">South Africa</span>
              <p class="text-xs text-stone-500">Johannesburg • Cape Town</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-3 rounded-lg">
              <span class="font-bold">Nigeria</span>
              <p class="text-xs text-stone-500">Lagos • Port Harcourt</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-3 rounded-lg">
              <span class="font-bold">Uganda</span>
              <p class="text-xs text-stone-500">Kampala</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-3 rounded-lg">
              <span class="font-bold">Tanzania</span>
              <p class="text-xs text-stone-500">Dar es Salaam</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Middle East -->
        <div
          id="middle-east"
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg scroll-mt-24"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <span class="text-7xl">🕌</span>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-stone-900">
              Middle East
            </h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-stone-700 mb-6">
            Dubai serves as our gateway to the Middle East, with growing demand
            for hibiscus, chillies, and organic herbs across the Gulf region.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <div class="bg-stone-50 p-3 rounded-lg">
              <span class="font-bold">UAE</span>
